176
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:07,260
Oh, I'm not letting you out.

177
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:09,250
I see...

178
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:29,160
Spiritual Message
Love Spring of Moth Scales

179
00:20:26,620 --> 00:20:28,580
Spiritual Message.

