00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:53,470
The ability he's using to separate
Pouf from the King.

182
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:57,640
If the third floor of the tower
is surrounded by smoke,

183
00:20:58,570 --> 00:21:00,710
the King and Pitou aren't there.

184
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:02,650
Where are they?

